<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="guide-vt">guide <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɡaɪd/    美 /ɡaɪd/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-lead">1.★ <strong>为…领路；带领 (lead)；引导：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>A young lady guided us on a tour of the museum.
一位年轻女士带领我们参观了博物馆。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Her warm heart would surely <strong>guide</strong> her <strong>in</strong> the right direction.
她的热心肠必定会引导她向正确的方向走。</p><footer>2015 重庆</footer></div></div>